[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":388},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fdocker\u002F20230122\u002F3483968861\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fdocker\u002F20230122\u002F3483968861\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fdocker\u002F20230122\u002F3483968861\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fdocker\u002F20230122\u002F3483968861\u002F":365,"related:\u002Fdocker\u002F20230122\u002F3483968861\u002F":374},"\u002Fen\u002Fdocker\u002F2023\u002F01\u002F22\u002Fstep-by-step-docker-dockerfile\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":347,"date":348,"description":18,"extension":349,"lang":350,"meta":351,"navigation":352,"path":353,"readingMinutes":354,"seo":355,"standalone":356,"stem":357,"tags":358,"tldr":361,"updated":362,"url":363,"__hash__":364},"content\u002F一步步掌握基礎 Docker\u002F2-一步步掌握基礎-Docker-DockerFile.md","(2)一步步掌握基礎 Docker - DockerFile","3483968861",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":332},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,26,30,33,38,45,48,64,67,71,74,83,88,104,111,120,123,138,145,148,157,160,164,185,194,198,201,210,213,226,230,237,246,249,264,274,278,281,284,288,291,300,306,310,313,322,325,328],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"接下來我們要來接去前一篇的後半部分，也就是關於 DockerFile 這個檔案。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"dockerfile-是什麼","DockerFile 是什麼？",[16,24,25],{},"DockerFile 簡單來講它是一個腳本檔案，這個腳本檔案會告訴 Docker 要做哪些事情進而建立出一個 Docker Image，所以其實 DockerFile 裡面有一些指令你必須要看得懂，這樣子你才會知道 Docker 在做什麼事情。",[12,27,29],{"id":28},"dockerfile-指令","DockerFile 指令",[16,31,32],{},"接下來我們要認識一些指令，如同前面所說，這些指令將會告訴 Docker 要做哪些事情",[34,35,37],"h3",{"id":36},"from","FROM",[16,39,40,41,44],{},"告知 Docker 我們目前要使用哪個 Image 作為基底，雖然前面有說明 Image 是映像檔的概念，所以 ",[42,43,37],"code",{}," 就是在告知 Docker 我們要使用哪個映像檔作為基底。",[16,46,47],{},"舉例來講，如果我們要使用 Node.js 16.15.0 的話，就要這樣寫",[49,50,55],"pre",{"className":51,"code":52,"language":53,"meta":54,"style":54},"language-dockerfile shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","FROM node:16.15.0\n","dockerfile","",[42,56,57],{"__ignoreMap":54},[58,59,62],"span",{"class":60,"line":61},"line",1,[58,63,52],{},[16,65,66],{},"這樣子 Docker 就會將環境指定 Node.js 16.15.0 了~",[34,68,70],{"id":69},"run","RUN",[16,72,73],{},"這個指令非常的簡單，其實就是告知 Docker 要執行哪些指令，如果是 Node.js 環境的話，然後你想要執行 app.js 那麼就這樣寫",[49,75,77],{"className":51,"code":76,"language":53,"meta":54,"style":54},"RUN node app.js\n",[42,78,79],{"__ignoreMap":54},[58,80,81],{"class":60,"line":61},[58,82,76],{},[16,84,85,87],{},[42,86,70],{}," 指令的概念就跟你在終端機輸入的行為是一樣的，只是環境變成在 Docker 底下做而已，因此如果是多行指令的話，可以這樣寫",[49,89,91],{"className":51,"code":90,"language":53,"meta":54,"style":54},"RUN npm install\nRUN npm run build\n",[42,92,93,98],{"__ignoreMap":54},[58,94,95],{"class":60,"line":61},[58,96,97],{},"RUN npm install\n",[58,99,101],{"class":60,"line":100},2,[58,102,103],{},"RUN npm run build\n",[16,105,106,107,110],{},"所以其實非常的簡單，但要注意一行指令只能執行一個指令，但你也可以同時執行多個指令，只要用 ",[42,108,109],{},"&&"," 連接就可以了",[49,112,114],{"className":51,"code":113,"language":53,"meta":54,"style":54},"RUN npm install && npm run build\n",[42,115,116],{"__ignoreMap":54},[58,117,118],{"class":60,"line":61},[58,119,113],{},[16,121,122],{},"當然你也有可能看到另一種寫法，也就是陣列形式的寫法",[49,124,126],{"className":51,"code":125,"language":53,"meta":54,"style":54},"RUN [\"npm\", \"install\"]\nRUN [\"npm\", \"run\", \"build\"]\n",[42,127,128,133],{"__ignoreMap":54},[58,129,130],{"class":60,"line":61},[58,131,132],{},"RUN [\"npm\", \"install\"]\n",[58,134,135],{"class":60,"line":100},[58,136,137],{},"RUN [\"npm\", \"run\", \"build\"]\n",[16,139,140,141,144],{},"這等價於 ",[42,142,143],{},"npm install 與 npm run build","，但是這樣寫的好處是可以避免 Docker 在執行指令的時候，因為你的指令中有空白而造成的錯誤。",[16,146,147],{},"那陣列寫法如果也要同時執行多個指令呢？這樣寫就可以了",[49,149,151],{"className":51,"code":150,"language":53,"meta":54,"style":54},"RUN [\"npm\", \"install\", \"&&\", \"npm\", \"run\", \"build\"]\n",[42,152,153],{"__ignoreMap":54},[58,154,155],{"class":60,"line":61},[58,156,150],{},[16,158,159],{},"有沒有瞬間看懂一些 Docker 指令了呢？",[34,161,163],{"id":162},"cmd","CMD",[16,165,166,167,169,170,172,173,175,176,178,179,181,182,184],{},"另外有一個跟 ",[42,168,70],{}," 很相似的指令，也就是 ",[42,171,163],{},"，但是 ",[42,174,163],{}," 跟 ",[42,177,70],{}," 的差別在於 ",[42,180,163],{}," 是在啟動 Container 的時候才會執行，而 ",[42,183,70],{}," 則是在建立 Image 的時候才會執行，因此兩者執行的時間點不同。",[16,186,187,188,190,191,193],{},"這一段應該會有點複雜，這邊先提一個觀念，Dockerfile 在執行時，會依據我們寫的內容一行一行的執行，執行完畢後會封裝成一個 Image，因此 ",[42,189,70],{}," 就會在封裝成 Image 的時候執行，而 ",[42,192,163],{}," 則是在啟動 Container 的時候才會執行。",[34,195,197],{"id":196},"copy","COPY",[16,199,200],{},"這個指令相對比較簡單，就是複製用的，假設你要複製一個檔案到 Docker 環境就這樣寫",[49,202,204],{"className":51,"code":203,"language":53,"meta":54,"style":54},"COPY .\u002Fapp.js \u002Fapp\u002Fapp.js\n",[42,205,206],{"__ignoreMap":54},[58,207,208],{"class":60,"line":61},[58,209,203],{},[16,211,212],{},"這一段指令就是將 app.js 複製到 \u002Fapp\u002Fapp.js 這個位置，這個位置是相對於 Docker 環境的位置。",[16,214,215,216,219,220,222,223,225],{},"但你有可能會看到另一個類似的指令，就是 ",[42,217,218],{},"ADD","，這個指令跟 ",[42,221,197],{}," 很類似，以官方建議來講 ",[42,224,218],{}," 已經不被建議使用了。",[34,227,229],{"id":228},"env","ENV",[16,231,232,233,236],{},"其實這個指令應該是滿常用的，就是設定環境變數的，假設我們要設定一個環境變數 ",[42,234,235],{},"NODE_ENV","，那麼就這樣寫",[49,238,240],{"className":51,"code":239,"language":53,"meta":54,"style":54},"ENV NODE_ENV production\n",[42,241,242],{"__ignoreMap":54},[58,243,244],{"class":60,"line":61},[58,245,239],{},[16,247,248],{},"多個 ENV 的話，可以這樣寫",[49,250,252],{"className":51,"code":251,"language":53,"meta":54,"style":54},"ENV NODE_ENV production \\\n    PORT 3000\n",[42,253,254,259],{"__ignoreMap":54},[58,255,256],{"class":60,"line":61},[58,257,258],{},"ENV NODE_ENV production \\\n",[58,260,261],{"class":60,"line":100},[58,262,263],{},"    PORT 3000\n",[16,265,266,267,269,270,273],{},"上面這一段就是設定了兩個環境變數，一個是 ",[42,268,235],{},"，另一個是 ",[42,271,272],{},"PORT","。",[34,275,277],{"id":276},"avg","AVG",[16,279,280],{},"AVG 與 ENV 也是非常相似，但是兩種運行的環境是不同的，一個是在建立 Image 的時候，另一個是在啟動 Container 的時候。",[16,282,283],{},"概念就像是全域變數跟區域變數，AVG 是全域變數，而 ENV 是區域變數。",[34,285,287],{"id":286},"expose","EXPOSE",[16,289,290],{},"這個指令也是滿常用的，就是告訴 Docker 這個容器會使用哪些 port，假設我們要使用 3000 這個 port，那麼就這樣寫",[49,292,294],{"className":51,"code":293,"language":53,"meta":54,"style":54},"EXPOSE 3000\n",[42,295,296],{"__ignoreMap":54},[58,297,298],{"class":60,"line":61},[58,299,293],{},[16,301,302,303,305],{},"為什麼要寫 ",[42,304,287],{}," 呢？因為如果你沒有寫，那麼 Docker 就不會知道這個容器會使用哪些 port，因此就會造成一些問題。",[34,307,309],{"id":308},"workdir","WORKDIR",[16,311,312],{},"這個指令是在指定我們工作目錄的位置，假設我們要指定工作目錄為 \u002Fapp，那麼就這樣寫",[49,314,316],{"className":51,"code":315,"language":53,"meta":54,"style":54},"WORKDIR \u002Fapp\n",[42,317,318],{"__ignoreMap":54},[58,319,320],{"class":60,"line":61},[58,321,315],{},[16,323,324],{},"接下來我們的指令都會在 \u002Fapp 這個目錄下執行。",[16,326,327],{},"那麼以上這幾個指令算是是我們比較常見的指令，當然還有其他的，但這邊就只需要知道這些就好。",[329,330,331],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":54,"searchDepth":100,"depth":100,"links":333},[334,335,336],{"id":14,"depth":100,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":100,"text":22},{"id":28,"depth":100,"text":29,"children":337},[338,340,341,342,343,344,345,346],{"id":36,"depth":339,"text":37},3,{"id":69,"depth":339,"text":70},{"id":162,"depth":339,"text":163},{"id":196,"depth":339,"text":197},{"id":228,"depth":339,"text":229},{"id":276,"depth":339,"text":277},{"id":286,"depth":339,"text":287},{"id":308,"depth":339,"text":309},"docker","2023-01-22 21:55:00","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fdocker\u002F2-docker-dockerfile","3",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"一步步掌握基礎 Docker\u002F2-一步步掌握基礎-Docker-DockerFile",[347,359,360],"一步步掌握基礎 Docker","Dockerfile",null,"2023-01-24 14:35:00","\u002Fdocker\u002F20230122\u002F3483968861\u002F","E58dU55a9zqCmB-Yqe2ydONfc2CmBGfaxDziQRbGFeQ",{"newer":366,"older":370},{"url":367,"title":368,"date":369},"\u002Fdocker\u002F20230123\u002F2896707023\u002F","(3)一步步掌握基礎 Docker - 小試身手","2023-01-23 21:20:00",{"url":371,"title":372,"date":373},"\u002Fdocker\u002F20230120\u002F1680751655\u002F","(1)一步步掌握基礎 Docker - Docker 是什麼？","2023-01-20 12:04:38",[375,379,384],{"url":376,"title":377,"date":378,"readingMinutes":354},"\u002Fdocker\u002F20241219\u002F2070727594\u002F","如何將 Vite+Vue 封裝到 Docker 並運行？","2024-12-19 16:36:18",{"url":380,"title":381,"date":382,"readingMinutes":383},"\u002Fdocker\u002F20230129\u002F1926467390\u002F","(11)一步步掌握基礎 Docker - 目錄","2023-01-29 15:22:19","1",{"url":385,"title":386,"date":387,"readingMinutes":383},"\u002Fdocker\u002F20230129\u002F345996692\u002F","(10)一步步掌握基礎 Docker - Docker GUI","2023-01-29 15:20:19",1784020342722]